### Sample API Requests for Testing

# Set environment variable
# @name = login

### Login API Test
POST {{baseUrl}}/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testpass"
}

###

### Get User Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/details HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Environment Variables (uncomment the one you want to use)
# @baseUrl = https://api.dev.example.com
@baseUrl = https://api.qa.example.com

### Sample Test with Query Parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Sample POST with JSON body
POST {{baseUrl}}/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "role": "user"
}

###

### Sample PUT request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/123 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe Updated",
    "email": "john.doe.updated@example.com"
}

